'''天主教洛德瓦爾教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Loduarinus}}；{{lang-sw|Jimbo Katoliki Lodwar}}）是[[肯亞|肯亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教基蘇木總教區|基蘇木總教區]]。

教區的前身是一個於1968年1月11日成立的[[宗座監牧區|宗座監牧區]]<ref>{{cite web |title=ELDORETENSIS (LODUARINAE) |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19680111_loduarinae.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117144713/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19680111_loduarinae.html |archivedate=2019-11-17 |language=la |date=1968-01-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1978年1月30日升為教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |year=1978 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=276-277 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-70-1978-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-02-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203114746/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-70-1978-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-02-03 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區位於[[圖爾卡納縣|圖爾卡納縣]]。2004年有48,759名教友（佔轄區總人口10.2%）、二十個堂區、五十七名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 16.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/16/0882/01840.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117130358/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/16/0882/01840.html |archivedate=2019-11-17 |language=it |date=2019-11-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|巴特利爵·哈靈頓 (主教)|Patrick Harrington (bishop)|巴特利爵·若瑟·哈靈頓}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 05.03.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/03/05/0135/00338.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117144056/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/03/05/0135/00338.html |archivedate=2019-11-17 |language=it |date=2011-03-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

